quran[24{c,v,t}:
53,45,aur yeh ke usi ne nar aur madah ka jora peda kya
53,46,aik boond se jab woh tapkai jati hai
53,47,aur yeh ke doosri zindagi bakhshna bhi usi ke zimma hai
53,48,aur yeh ke usi ne ghanni kya aur jaidaad bakhsh
53,49,aur yeh ke wohi sheri ka rab hai
53,50,aur yeh ke usi ne Aad-e- Owlaa ko halaak kya
53,51,aur samood ko aisa mitaya ke un mein se kisi ko baqi nah chorra
53,52,aur unn se pehlay qoum Nooh ko tabah kya kyunkay woh thay hi sakht zalim o sarkash log
53,53,aur ondhee girnay wali bustiyon ko utha phenka
53,54,phir chhaa diya unn par woh kuch jo ( tum jantay hi ho ke ) kya chhaa diya
53,55,"pas ae mukhatib, apne rab ki kin kin nematon mein to shak kere ga? """
53,56,yeh aik tanbeeh hai pehlay aayi hui tnbihat mein se
53,57,anay wali gharri qareeb aa lagi hai
53,58,Allah ke siwa koi uss ko hata ne wala nahi
53,59,ab kya yahi woh baatein hain jin par tum izhaar taajjub karte ho ?
53,60,hanstay ho aur rotay nahi ho ?
53,61,aur ga baja kar inhen talte ho ?
53,62,jhuk jao Allah ke agay aur bandagi baja lao
54,1,qayamat ki gharri qareeb aa gayi aur chaand phatt gaya
54,2,magar inn logon ka haal yeh hai ke khuwa koi nishani dekh len mun mourr jatay hain aur kehte hain yeh to chalta howa jaadoo hai
54,3,unhon ne ( is ko bhi ) jhutla diya aur apni khwahisaat nafs hi ki pairwi ki har maamla ko aakhir-kaar aik injaam par poanch kar rehna hai
54,4,inn logon ke samnay ( pichli qomon ke ) woh halaat aa chuke hain jin mein sar kashi se baz rakhnay ke liye kaafi samaan Ibrat hai
54,5,aur aisi hikmat jo nasiyaat ke maqsad ko badarja atam poora karti hai magar tnbihat inn par kargar nahi hoten
54,6,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se rukh phair lau jis roz pukarnay wala aik sakht nagawaar cheez ki taraf pukare ga"
